metadata.name: source-test-mozlint-codespell

command:
:: sccache currently uses the full compiler commandline as input to the
:: cache hash key, so create a symlink to the task dir and build from
:: the symlink dir to get consistent paths.
if exist z:\build rmdir z:\build

"c:\Program Files\Mercurial\hg.exe" robustcheckout --sharebase y:\hg-shared --purge --upstream https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-unified --revision f3776c9bb37a519d7f1c7d29408286fa93eedc3a https://hg.mozilla.org/try .\build\src

c:\mozilla-build\python\python.exe .\build\src\testing\mozharness\scripts\fx_desktop_build.py --config builds\releng_base_firefox.py --config builds\taskcluster_base_windows.py --config builds\taskcluster_base_win64.py --config builds\taskcluster_sub_win64\opt.py --branch try --skip-buildbot-actions --work-dir %cd:Z:=z:%\build --append-env-variables-from-configs
